> FAQ

Why sell it cheap?

I process a large number of cards each month that transform into many items that need to sell. The only way is to sell them at half price. Are illegally obtained goods and there is some risk if sell on sites like eBay (they request invoices etc).

How does the shipping?

I ship worldwide with registered mail ($35) or DHL ($65). All packages are sent with tracking code.

Escrow & Payment method

You can pay with bitcoins, perfectmoney or any clearnet bitcoin escrow if you prefer the transaction with Escrow. 100% Escrow accepted (including shipping). I do not accept other payment method.

Are original?

All items are 100% original. In the original box.

The phones are Unlocked?

Are Factory unlocked. And GSM models to work worldwide.

How are purchased the items?

We recharged visa giftcards with the "illegal" cards. Bought amazon giftcards with them and finally buy the items. Is difficult for any company trace from the initial card to the item.

Will I be charged customs taxes?

Maybe. We declare as "broken for repair" or similar statements based in the country (and a lower value). This may avoid customs taxes. We can also cover the customs taxes for bulk orders.
